Package: DadaNanoBC
Type: Package
Title: DADA2-Based Pipeline for Infering DNA Barcodes from Nanopore Sequence Data 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Markus", "Schlegel",
      email = "markschl19@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3453-4783")
    )
  )
Description: This package provides functions and a targets pipeline workflow
    to infer specimen barcodes from Nanopore sequencing data with multiplexed samples.
    It includes functions for automatic taxonomic assignments and
    taxonomy-based recognition of contaminants.
URL: https://github.com/markschl/DadaNanoBC, https://markschl.github.io/DadaNanoBC
